---------------------<br>
<br>
Hello everyone! I bring to ya this new mod i made, Black &amp; White 2 Plus=
!<br>
<br>
This was born as a simple basic mod to improve the main campaign, but end u=
p being a super massive mod that grows every day with new content!<br>
<br>
This mod does... well, lots of things.<br>
<br>
- This mod does not reconvert the main campaign, in fact, this mod improves=
 it!<br>
<br>
- I do respect the original game, so i'm sticking with the original idea, a=
ll lands are vanilla with small touches around to preserve the original asp=
ect of the game!<br>
<br>
- Added a ton of rebalance to the game, this will make the game harder, but=
 fair if you know hot to play! you will have to learn everything about army=
 units, also use startegy to build your city with separation of indusrial, =
reisdential, impressiveness and worshipping zones!<br>
<br>
- Infinite ore from every mine! Yes but now all buildings costs a lot to bu=
ild! make good use of your builders and factories to get all resources you =
can!<br>
<br>
- Slightly improved enemy AI (not too much, i made them dumb on purpose for=
 progression!<br>
<br>
- Two new main campaign lands! A second (third if you count tutorial) norse=
 land! the norse homeland awaits you! Also included a new scrapped land to =
fix a huge plot hole about aztec sacrifices! The second aztec sacrificial l=
ands in wich you have to rescue prisoners before they sacrifice them all!<b=
r>
<br>
- A new post game: After defeating the aztecs, return to your now greek hom=
eland! (The land in wich aztec assault happened), now recovered from the at=
tack, from here you can play any of the previous lands with you fully grown=
 creature!<br>
<br>
- From the Greek homeland you can now have access to the new campaign: Old =
gods lands!<br>
<br>
---------------------------------------------------------------------------=
------------------------<br>
<br>
Old gods lands is the first expansion of Black &amp; White 2 Plus, wich inc=
ludes 9 new lands to explore, a new story, new miracles and a new god!<br>
<br>
- The lands are the black &amp; White 1 lands, their skirmishes and sotry o=
nes, travel back to these ancient legendary lands to uncover a new conflict=
 and become more powerful!<br>
<br>
- Get a new giant temple just like the ancient lands and get new miracles, =
all unlcoked as you progress trought these lands! (Miracles like food, wood=
, megablast, decay, all Battle fo the gods and other miracles will unlocked=
 as you progress!)<br>
<br>
- A new deity, a menace you have never faced before await you on old gods l=
ands, a powerful demonic god that not event the ancient god could stop!<br>
<br>
There are lot of new surprises on this mod, I'm currently working on a new =
expansion, Elementals, wich will continue the story after old gods lands ex=
pansion!<br>
<br>
The mod is completed and fully playable from start to finish! i amde lots o=
f testing to seek crashes, while some could be found around becasue of game=
 limitations, these are very rare to find! but anyways, save just in case!<=
br>
<br>
The mod is just... too big! CHECK THE README (PLEASE!) to see all changes!<=
br>
<br>
More information on moddb:  <a href=3D"https://www.moddb.com/mods/black-whi=
te-2-plus" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"link link--external" rel=3D"nofollow =
ugc noopener">https://www.moddb.com/mods/black-white-2-plus</a><br>
<br>
<br>
Just in case, installation instructions:<br>
<br>
- Install Black &amp; white 2<br>
- Install both v1.1 and v1.2 patches<br>
- Install Black &amp; White 2 PLUS V1.0 (this is the base mod, v1.42 and 4g=
b patch are applied!)<br>
- Install Black &amp; White 2 PLUS V1.4 (this fixes all bugs and fixes all =
stability, do not install previous patches!)<br>
<br>
I hope you enjoy this mod! Working on the next expansion! will post it here=
 when i finish it! ^^<br>
<br>
Also i have a patreon, just for tips: <a href=3D"https://www.patreon.com/c/=
BWBluCreations" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"link link--external" rel=3D"nofo=
llow ugc noopener">https://www.patreon.com/c/BWBluCreations</a><br>
<br>
<br>
Thank you, everyone who is a fan of this awesome game &lt;3<br>
